{"tid":138881,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（自學日文）一齊分享下點練日語說話","createTime":"2017-03-01T03:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T16:09:23.000Z","uid":54009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12f5bbc0844aa7bc0dc4cbb101a9e7e0bad94d8a","tid":138881,"uid":54009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"自學左一排日文，讀同聽都唔算難練，但講野方面無人可以交流真係好難練到。暫時自學黎講，我覺得用shadowing嘅方法練應該最好，但奈何搵唔到有日文版嘅voicetube<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以分享下類似嘅app/邊啲日本節目可以拎黎模仿（最好見到咀形）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jpmarumaru.com/tw/JPSongList.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpmarumaru.com%2Ftw%2FJPSongList.asp&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ac4db18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jpmarumaru.com/tw/JPSongList.asp</a><br />\n練日文歌一流<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gavo.t.u-tokyo.ac.jp/ojad/phrasing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gavo.t.u-tokyo.ac.jp%2Fojad%2Fphrasing&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=11f1a5b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gavo.t.u-tokyo.ac.jp/ojad/phrasing</a><br />\n呢個網可以copy句子入去，讀出黎時會標埋重音，同埋可以DL落黎"},{"pid":"3e2513e987b098feb6b6869d11cdbd465be14c7d","tid":138881,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"平日番學果陣講"},{"pid":"1f3e1d9b7faac4e653e090f545502d2798271ac9","tid":138881,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"邊度有得學文法? 例如敬語, 叮嚀語, 過去式等等<br />\n<br />\n3月先開始上當但係之前都係自己睇"},{"pid":"8864c01c840157dbca499f03984f03cb94391d68","tid":138881,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"ケモのフレンズ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2722e24cb113bead65a596a205db150a9fe